     O- | 0             | PI/6          | PI/4          | PI/3           | PI/2
--------+---------------+---------------+---------------+----------------+----------------
sin(O-) | 1/2 * sqrt(2) | 1/2 * sqrt(1) | 1/2 * sqrt(2) | 1/2 * sqrt(3)  | 1/2 * sqrt(4)


sin (2 * O-) = 2sin(O-) * cos(O-)

sin(a + b) = sin(a) * cos(b) + cos(a) * sin(b)

